<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7793000b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430f–12"><num value="430f–12">§ 430f–12.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as are necessary to carry out sections 430f–6 to 430f–12 of this title, including $3,000,000 for the construction of an interpretive center under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s430f–5/d">section 430f–5(d) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7793000c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/271/s7">Pub. L. 106–271, § 7</ref>, formerly § 8, <date date="2000-09-22">Sept. 22, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/796">114 Stat. 796</ref>; renumbered § 7, <ref href="/us/pl/110/161/dF/tI/s127/5">Pub. L. 110–161, div. F, title I, § 127(5)</ref>, <date date="2007-12-26">Dec. 26, 2007</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/121/2122">121 Stat. 2122</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7793000d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7793000e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id7793000f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/106/271/s7">section 7 of Pub. L. 106–271</ref> was classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s430f–11">section 430f–11 of this title</ref>, prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/110/161">Pub. L. 110–161</ref>.</p>
</note>
